<plot>In each episode, well-reputed lawyer Ben Deman (hence the title), Flanders' closest equivalent of Matlock, takes and pleads the case of an accused before the Court of Assises (a non-permanent Belgian criminal court without appeal), usually for murder. Before the actual court trial he also investigates, helped by a team of legal staff and private detective; his and their private lives may provide minor plot lines.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?136077</url></doc>
